name: Brian Raper
text: Great place to go to. The fun lady from Alaska helped me out. She took the time to talk to me and find out what I was wanting so she could offer suggestions. I hope to go back soon and look forward to seeing her there. Great atmosphere inside and nice selection to things as well. All around good place to shop.
